{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ff18f71d3c","title":"对杨寅田大字报的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e76f166eab","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":null,"articleId":"ff18f71d3c"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b8f86c117a","type":"paragraph","text":"生的文化大革命行动看来，我不相信有正民主，正克思主义，而是站在资产阶级方面反对无产阶级文化大革命。团中央不仅不支持青年学生运动，反而压学生运动，我看该处理。","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"ff18f71d3c"},{"id":"22883c4e60","type":"paragraph","text":"炮打司合部","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"ff18f71d3c"},{"id":"d63b6c2140","type":"paragraph","text":"我的一张大字报","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"ff18f71d3c"},{"id":"677cb97ca6","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年八月五日）","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"ff18f71d3c"},{"id":"545f2c6d9a","type":"paragraph","text":"全国第一张马列主义的大字报和《人民日报》评论员的评论，写得何等好呵！腊同志们重读一通这张大字报和这个评论。可是在五十多天里，从中央到地方的某些领导同志，却反其道而行之，站在反动的资产阶级立场上，实行资产阶级专政，将无产阶级轰轰烈烈的文化大革命运动打下去，倒是非，混潘黑白，围剩革命派，压制不同意见，实行白色恐饰，自以为得意，长资产阶级的威风，灭无产阶级的志气，又何其毒也！联系到一九六二年的右倾和一九六四年的形“左”而实右的错澳倾向，自不是可以发人深醒的吗？","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"ff18f71d3c"},{"id":"cc79fdc6ce","type":"paragraph","text":"毛东在修改《欢呼北大的一张大字报》","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"ff18f71d3c"},{"id":"411ab5184f","type":"paragraph","text":"一文时加的一段器","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"ff18f71d3c"},{"id":"0bf4fa6f42","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年八月五日）","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"ff18f71d3c"},{"id":"1e253ed5ac","type":"paragraph","text":"危害革命的错识领导，不应当无条件接受，而应当坚决抵制。在这次文化大革命中，广大革命师生及革命干部对于错误的领导，就广泛地进行过抵制","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"ff18f71d3c"},{"id":"75aebe903c","type":"paragraph","text":"在中共中央基众接待站的斋","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"ff18f71d3c"},{"id":"eaf0b5c893","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年八月十日）你们要关心国家大事，要把无产阶级文化大革命进行到底！","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"ff18f71d3c"},{"id":"a6402a8049","type":"paragraph","text":"对檬黄田大字报的批示","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"ff18f71d3c"},{"id":"52c1d1eb35","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年八月）印发全会（指十一中全会）各同志。将杨寅田大字报题目用特号字，全文用老五号刊出。","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"ff18f71d3c"},{"id":"982871d4c1","type":"paragraph","text":"·267","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"ff18f71d3c"}],"page":{"id":"7f9745bea9","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"ff18f71d3c","start":280,"end":280}}}},"__N_SSG":true}